
1) Open this file in notepad, Windows 11
2) Make sure the font size is small enough to fit at least 44 lines and 
   90 characters in the screen

4) **MOST IMPORTANT STEP**:
   a)  in line 44 bellow, there is a line marker (---------)
   c) Resize the notepad window such that the line marker is exactly at the bottom of
      the screen. i.e. If you made the window any smaller,
      the line marker would disappear.
      Be as exact as you can. Make sure the cursor is on line 1 during the resizing.
5) Now, press and hold the page-down button.
